text: Þis is þara VIII hida boc æt embresham.
Þe eadgar cing gæbocode gode & sanctæ andree in to meone on ece yrfæ.
Ðis synt þa landgemero to æmbresham þara VIII hida ærest on ummanig of ummanig on mearcdene.
Of mearcdene on þone ealdan fald.
Of þam ealdan falde on manning stan.
Of þam burnan on ultres denu of þære denu on id hilde stan.
Of fearndune on bunning fald of bunning falde on æcscfald.
Of æscfalde on smeagel hyrst of smeagel hyrste on wufincg fald.
Of sihter wic on slywhyrst of slywhyrste on umman ig.
